title: `cargo doc` panic (No resolutions for a doc link)

labels.name: T-rustdoc
labels.description: Relevant to the rustdoc team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

labels.name: A-intra-doc-links
labels.description: Area: Intra-doc links, the ability to link to items in docs by name

labels.name: S-has-mcve
labels.description: A Minimal Complete and Verifiable Example has been found for this issue
